  <description>
    <p>
      Office-GTK4 wraps Microsoft 365 Online (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, OneNote,
      Outlook) in a native GTK4 / libadwaita window using WebKitGTK. Sessions
      and cookies are persisted so you stay logged in between launches.
    </p>
